          "plain_text": "Haris comes to take us to get SIM cards. It’s an elaborate process these days with a long queue. Bless Niklas as he got our tickets for us. We arrived to a Nik who has been traveling for close to 48 hours and wants nothing more than to arrive at the hostel. ",
